OL,6,FTeachers will vote on whether the NEU,
OL,7,Fthe largest teaching union in the UK,
OL,8,Fshould lobby political parties ahead
OL,9,Fof the next general election to
OL,10,Fendorse its campaign to "replace
OL,11,FOfsted".
OL,13,FA motion, due to be debated on
OL,14,FWednesday, says the union should
OL,15,Fsupport members in "balloting for, and
OL,16,Ftaking, strike action" when
OL,17,F"mocksteds", deep-dives and excessive
OL,18,Fworkload have arisen through Ofsted
OL,19,Fpressures.
