OL,3,CFour out of five teachers say new
OL,4,Cinspection system is needed
OL,6,FIt comes after Ofsted has come under
OL,7,Fgreater scrutiny after the suicide of
OL,8,Fheadteacher Ruth Perry.
OL,10,FMrs Perry took her own life after an
OL,11,FOfsted report downgraded her Caversham
OL,12,FPrimary School in Reading, Berkshire,
OL,13,Ffrom its highest rating to its lowest
OL,14,Fover safeguarding concerns.
OL,16,FProfessor Julia Waters, the sister of
OL,17,FMrs Perry, is due to address the NEU's
OL,18,Fannual conference on Friday.
