OL,4,Cinspection system is needed
OL,6,FThe survey, carried out between
OL,7,FFebruary 6 and 20, suggests only 3% of
OL,8,Fteachers believe Ofsted acts as a
OL,9,F"reliable and trusted arbiter of
OL,10,Fstandards" and just 4% believe it acts
OL,11,Findependently of Government.
OL,13,FMore than four in five (82%) agreed
OL,14,Fwith a statement that said Ofsted has
OL,15,Fso many problems that it "would be
OL,16,Fbetter to start afresh with a new
OL,17,Fsystem of inspection".
