OL,4,Cinspection system is needed
OL,6,FOne respondent said, "Ofsted has
OL,7,Fcreated toxic environments, resulting
OL,8,Fin damaging pressure on staff and
OL,9,Fending the careers of excellent staff."
OL,11,FAnother respondent, who cried after
OL,12,Fspeaking to an Ofsted inspector in the
OL,13,Flast academic year, said, "I was
OL,14,Fabsolutely petrified that I would say
OL,15,Fsomething wrong and let the school and
OL,16,Fmy colleagues down. I felt so stressed
OL,17,Fand overwhelmed by the process."
