OL,6,FLast month, Sir Martyn Oliver, chief
OL,7,Finspector of Ofsted, launched the
OL,8,Fwatchdog's Big Listen public
OL,9,Fconsultation which will seek views
OL,10,Fabout Ofsted.
OL,12,FIn his first major speech since
OL,13,Fbecoming chief inspector in January,
OL,14,FSir Martyn said he wanted to "mark a
OL,15,Fnew chapter" with the sector, adding
OL,16,Fthat "nothing is off the table".
