OL,6,FDaniel Kebede, joint general secretary
OL,7,Fof the NEU, said, "Ofsted is out of
OL,8,Ftouch and out of favour. As this
OL,9,Fsurvey shows, the inspectorate's
OL,10,Freputation has worsened since we last
OL,11,Fsought members' views in 2022."
OL,13,F"No amount of rebranding will
OL,14,Feradicate the entrenched view that
OL,15,FOfsted's days are numbered. If it ever
OL,16,Fcommanded respect, those days are now
OL,17,Flong gone."
